snippet.title: Official Scribblenauts Showdown Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Starting March 6th, play the coolest party game modes on Scribblenauts Showdown, where up to four players can face off with 25+ of the coolest mini games. Coming to Nintendo Switch™, PlayStation® and Xbox One®. Don’t miss a beat, be sure to #ReadySetParty!
